The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation
		 Wednesday, March 26, 2003 				 Man gets death for dowry killing
																								Hyderabad, March 25: A court in Warangal has delivered a path-breaking judgment in a case of dowry harassment, sentencing a man to death for burning his wife and his parents to life imprisonment for abetting the crime, reports our special correspondent.																								Third additional sessions judge Mohan Gandhi yesterday awarded capital punishment to K. Madhav Reddy for dousing his wife, Kalavathi, with kerosene and burning her to death on April 20, 2000. 
